/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The street is lined with lush greenery, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Overhead, a network of power lines crisscrosses the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The sky itself is a clear blue, with the sun shining brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene.
